  "title": "Taekwondo Coach (Full time/Part Time)",
  "description": "<p>Kicks Taekwondo is currently recruiting full-time or part time coaches to join our coaching team.</p><p></p><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>To conduct lessons within a safe & supportive learning environment</p><p>To provide individual or group lessons</p><p>To facilitate regular & sparring classes</p><p>Constant feedback on students’ progress</p><p>Good communication skills and positive attitude</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>Minimum 1st Dan STF / Kukkiwon certificate</p><p>Coaching certification and relevant experience will be an added advantage</p><p>Ability to instruct, demonstrate and correct all color belts. Able to perform the same for black belt poomsae will be an added advantage.</p><p>Candidates without teaching experience are welcome to apply.</p><p></p><p>Working Hours: To be discussed during interview</p><p>Working Location: Upper Thomson or Ang Mo Kio</p><p></p><p>Salary will be commensurate with experience and discussed upon interview.</p><p></p><p>Interested candidates please contact kicksthomson@gmail.com with your resume and relevant work experience/qualifications.</p>",
