    "uen": "202309883W",
    "description": "<p>Welcome to Kicks Taekwondo, where our school is more than a place to train—it’s a second home for our students. We provide a safe, fun, and supportive environment that fosters both learning and personal growth.</p><p>At Kicks Taekwondo, we take pride in our close-knit community, bringing together people from all walks of life. Many parents entrust us with their children, not just to develop self-defense skills and confidence but to instill values that will guide them through life’s challenges.</p><p>Our training goes beyond perfecting punches and kicks. We emphasize discipline, resilience, and integrity, shaping individuals who are ready to excel both on and off the mat.</p>",
